  "about_item": [
    "Chew Proof Design: This raised cot bed has a solid aluminum frame that protects all vulnerable spots from chewing. Practically indestructible, it’s the only bed that will hold up against the most persistent or destructive of chewers, especially those that chew heavily from anxiety or boredom.",
    "Durable Ripstop Ballistic Bed Sling: This heavy-duty fabric features a dense weave (1200D) of thick fibers to withstand punctures and tears from scratching, digging, and chewing. It’s also resistant to dirt, fur, odor, and water, making it both easy to clean and a great elevated bed for use inside the home and outside.",
    "Sturdy Crate Bed: This bed is also sized to fit inside standard wire crates, making it perfect for dogs that chew or dig heavily from separation anxiety or boredom. Installation is easy - just slide it through the door at an angle and level it out once it’s inside. Double check your crate's inner dimensions before ordering, as crate manufacturers often round up their sizes.",
    "No Assembly Required: Unlike other elevated cot beds, the Chew Proof Armored Elevated Dog Bed arrives at your door already assembled, saving you the time and effort of having to put it together. Simply pop the legs into their sockets and the bed is all set for use!",
    "Non-skid Feet: The legs of the beds have soft foot pads on the bottom. These keep the bed from sliding, and also serve to protect hardwood, LVP, concrete, and other smooth flooring from damage."
